title: JUNKFOOD FONT?

Try [Keep on Truckin’](http://web.archive.org/web/20090503110006/http:/www.dafont.com/font.php?file=keep_on_truckin_fw&page=1&nb_ppp_old=10&text=Junk+Food+Loves+FREES&nb_ppp=10&psize=m&classt=alpha) by Brain Eaters Font Co. Free for personal use.
